overview: Nuclear Blast release with 81 music videos (clocking in at over six hours), incl. some clips from the label's new sublabel, Arising Empire, f.e. from IMMINENCE, NOVELISTS, and GWLT.  Otherwise the spectrum ranges from heavyweights such as NIGHTWISH, SLAYER, SABATON, LAMB OF GOD, MACHINE HEAD, AVANTASIA, HELLOWEEN, ACCEPT as well as Punk and Harcore acts like THE EXPLOITED, DISCHARGE, AGNOSTIC FRONT - a visual encyclopedia covering every genre of metal.
title: Monsters of Metal Vol. 10
